    "description": "Light, fluffy, and perfectly golden pancakes that are quick to make. The secret is in the buttermilk and not overmixing the batter.",
    "images": ["/images/recipes/pancakes-1.jpg"],
    "prepTime": 5,
    "cookTime": 15,
    "totalTime": 20,
    "servings": 4,
    "difficulty": "easy",
    "ingredients": [
